Question: An image contains a sitting baboon who is holding a roundish, yellowish fruit.

Reference Answer: True

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image contain a sitting baboon?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image contain a sitting baboon?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the baboon holding a roundish, yellowish fruit?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the baboon holding a roundish, yellowish fruit?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
